org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwLogical.HwComputing

Interface HwPLD

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComputingResource, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwComputingResource, HwResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ProcessingResource, Resource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwPLDImpl

    public interface HwPLD
extends HwComputingResource
    A representation of the model object 'Hw PLD'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Technology
    • Organization
    • Nb LU Ts
    • Nd LUT Inputs
    • Nb Flip Flops
    • Blocks RAM
    • Blocks Computing
    See Also:
    HwComputingPackage.getHwPLD()
